These are Puzzles for 5x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-1-1::.
There 2 different types of food: peas, pomegranate
There are 2 different favourite colors: blue, emerald
2 different pets are kept: mouse, rat
House: art-deco, wooden
The people use 2 different means of transport: jet-ski, train
1. the person eating pomegranate is on the right of the wooden house##1
2. the person eating peas is on the left of the person driving the train##1
3. the person who likes emerald is the owner of the mouse##1
4. the person who likes blue is the person eating peas##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |
| Food    | peas       | pomegranate  |
| Color         | blue | emerald |
| Pet         | rat        | mouse     |
| House       | wooden     | art-deco  |
| Transport   | jet-ski    | train     |

