.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-1-2::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: august, march
City: hamburg, paris
2 different pets are kept: ferret, goldfish
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: lacrosse, skateboarding
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: marigold, sunflower
1. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
2. the person who growsmarigold is on the far right##1
3. the owner of the ferret is the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
4. the owner of the ferret is the person who's birthday is in march##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |       2       |
| Birthday    | august  | march        |
| City         | paris | hamburg     |
| Pet         | goldfish  | ferret        |
| Sport       | lacrosse  | skateboarding |
| Flower   | sunflower      | marigold        |

