.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-1-3::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: daisy, aconite
The people have 2 different hobbies: camping, collecting
There are 2 different nationalities: spanish, american
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: electronic, pop
City: nizza, rome
1. the person who growsaconite is on the far left##1
2. the fan of pop is on the right of the spanish##1
3. the fan of electronic is on the left of the person traveling to nizza##1
4. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |    2     |
| Flower          | aconite             | daisy  |
| Hobby         | collecting         | camping  |
| Nationality           | spanish | american  |
| Music-Genre   | electronic         | pop      |
| City         | rome      | nizza |

