.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-1-4::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, game
There are 2 different favourite colors: black, amber
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: comedy, family
There are 2 different nationalities: chinese, turkish
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: rugby, swimming
1. the game-smoker is on the far right##1
2. the chinese is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
3. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
4. the person who likes amber is on the right of the person who likes black##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |
| Cigar          | davidoff    | game     |
| Color           | black   | amber |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy   | family     |
| Nationality   | chinese  | turkish    |
| Sport     | rugby | swimming       |

