2 different pets are kept: dog, rat
House: gothic-revival, cottage
1. the fan of trance is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
2. the gothic-revival house is the polish##1
3. the owner of the rat is on the left of the polish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Nationality         | colombian     | polish |
| Beverage   | tea | juice   |
| Music-Genre   | trance      | hip-hop |
| Pet           | rat         | dog     |
| House         | cottage  | gothic-revival |

 